1
00:00:10,980 --> 00:00:13,680
(International Hotel)

2
00:00:13,760 --> 00:00:15,200
(Jingshi Police Department)

3
00:00:15,248 --> 00:00:15,900
Chief Yuan.

4
00:00:15,900 --> 00:00:16,656
Young Master Zhao.

5
00:00:17,140 --> 00:00:18,220
How was the body found?

6
00:00:18,220 --> 00:00:20,352
Last night, Madam Zhang knocked,
but no one answered.

7
00:00:20,368 --> 00:00:21,220
If Mr. Zhang

8
00:00:21,220 --> 00:00:22,380
weren't staying out,

9
00:00:22,380 --> 00:00:23,500
he'd never sleep this early.

10
00:00:23,680 --> 00:00:24,740
Madam Zhang got worried,

11
00:00:24,740 --> 00:00:26,288
so she told me to unlock the door.

12
00:00:27,060 --> 00:00:27,660
Hurry up.

13
00:00:27,660 --> 00:00:29,300
What's taking you so long?

14
00:00:29,300 --> 00:00:30,220
Chengcai!

15
00:00:31,860 --> 00:00:33,860
=Cases Between Us=

16
00:00:33,860 --> 00:00:34,660
Chengcai!

17
00:00:35,780 --> 00:00:36,980
It's me.

18
00:00:36,980 --> 00:00:38,540
=Episode 17=

19
00:00:38,540 --> 00:00:39,420
Chengcai!

20
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:28,820
After the body was found,
did anyone else enter the room?

21
00:01:28,900 --> 00:01:29,540
No.

22
00:01:29,660 --> 00:01:31,580
As soon as Madam Zhang left,
I sealed the room

23
00:01:31,580 --> 00:01:32,740
and had

24
00:01:32,740 --> 00:01:33,700
these two attendants

25
00:01:33,700 --> 00:01:34,860
guard the door.

26
00:01:37,260 --> 00:01:39,580
(Xinghua Village, Baoquanyi Fen Liquor)
Baoquanyi?

27
00:01:39,780 --> 00:01:40,340
Well, well.

28
00:01:40,340 --> 00:01:41,660
A fifteen-year-old Fen liquor

29
00:01:41,660 --> 00:01:42,660
isn't easy to come by.

30
00:01:43,300 --> 00:01:44,780
Miss Bai gave it to Mr. Zhang

31
00:01:44,780 --> 00:01:46,420
as a wedding gift

32
00:01:46,620 --> 00:01:48,140
three years ago.

33
00:01:48,140 --> 00:01:49,700
It's been kept in our bar ever since.

34
00:01:50,140 --> 00:01:52,380
Mr. Zhang opened it tonight.

35
00:01:53,260 --> 00:01:54,900
I suppose he wanted
to drink to Miss Bai.

36
00:01:55,300 --> 00:01:57,020
Funny how he got sentimental
after she died.

37
00:01:58,448 --> 00:02:00,976
How many times did you see Zhang
Chengcai after he came back?

38
00:02:01,260 --> 00:02:01,820
Three.

39
00:02:02,180 --> 00:02:03,620
The first was at 9 PM.

40
00:02:03,620 --> 00:02:05,900
He called the front desk
and asked me to bring up ice.

41
00:02:05,900 --> 00:02:07,140
The second was at 10 PM.

42
00:02:07,140 --> 00:02:08,980
He said it wasn't enough
and asked for more.

43
00:02:08,980 --> 00:02:10,660
Then he told me to bring another bucket

44
00:02:10,660 --> 00:02:11,700
at 11 PM.

45
00:02:11,900 --> 00:02:13,300
The third time was at 11 PM.

46
00:02:30,980 --> 00:02:32,180
The lividity is bright red.

47
00:02:33,020 --> 00:02:33,620
Patchy.

48
00:02:33,744 --> 00:02:34,780
Mostly across the back.

49
00:02:34,780 --> 00:02:35,660
It hasn't spread yet.

50
00:02:36,420 --> 00:02:37,780
The lividity was still developing.

51
00:02:38,020 --> 00:02:39,260
So he couldn't have been dead

52
00:02:39,260 --> 00:02:40,640
for more than two to four hours.

53
00:02:40,816 --> 00:02:42,800
That puts the time of death
between 11 PM and 1 AM.

54
00:02:43,140 --> 00:02:44,220
But lividity at this stage

55
00:02:44,220 --> 00:02:45,500
is usually dark red.

56
00:02:46,020 --> 00:02:47,380
His is bright red.

57
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:48,304
Bright-red lividity

58
00:02:48,310 --> 00:02:49,820
is one of the classic signs of drowning.

59
00:02:51,180 --> 00:02:52,220
He got drunk,

60
00:02:52,780 --> 00:02:54,540
slipped into the tub, and drowned.

61
00:02:54,900 --> 00:02:56,780
Well. Getting drunk and taking a bath

62
00:02:56,780 --> 00:02:57,940
is just asking for trouble.

63
00:02:58,500 --> 00:02:59,380
Can you verify this?

64
00:03:05,220 --> 00:03:06,060
Give me a hand.

65
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:06,980
Turn him over.

66
00:03:14,950 --> 00:03:16,832
His lungs aren't swollen

67
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:18,170
or showing any fluid buildup.

68
00:03:18,220 --> 00:03:20,000
That suggests
that once the victim is dead,

69
00:03:20,048 --> 00:03:21,500
breathing and blood circulation stop,

70
00:03:21,500 --> 00:03:22,990
so the water couldn't enter the lungs.

71
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,980
He died first, then ended up in the tub?

72
00:03:24,980 --> 00:03:25,950
That's what it looks like.

73
00:03:25,968 --> 00:03:27,616
There was no swelling or foreign matter

74
00:03:27,616 --> 00:03:28,704
in his mouth, nasal passages,

75
00:03:28,780 --> 00:03:29,980
lungs, or bronchi.

76
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:30,980
And no fluid either.

77
00:03:32,100 --> 00:03:33,180
What killed him?

78
00:03:33,728 --> 00:03:35,900
(Xinghua Village Baoquanyi Fen Liquor)
I noticed baijiu and ice.

79
00:03:36,060 --> 00:03:38,060
Baijiu over ice can trigger

80
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:39,460
a sudden hypoglycemic collapse,

81
00:03:39,500 --> 00:03:40,980
which may lead to sudden cardiac death.

82
00:03:41,020 --> 00:03:43,580
Why were the lividity marks bright red?

83
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,980
Bright-red lividity can indicate
carbon monoxide poisoning

84
00:03:45,980 --> 00:03:48,700
or cyanide poisoning.

85
00:03:50,860 --> 00:03:52,540
If he was poisoned,

86
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:54,540
then someone staged the drowning

87
00:03:54,540 --> 00:03:56,300
to conceal the real cause of death.

88
00:03:56,540 --> 00:03:58,300
Zhang Chengcai died

89
00:03:58,300 --> 00:04:00,260
between 11 PM and 1 AM.

90
00:04:00,540 --> 00:04:01,700
Which means

91
00:04:01,700 --> 00:04:04,180
someone entered the room
during that window

92
00:04:04,980 --> 00:04:06,300
and moved the body.

93
00:04:08,496 --> 00:04:09,696
I can't take the body.

94
00:04:09,744 --> 00:04:12,140
Can I take the blood samples
and the liquor back for testing?

95
00:04:12,660 --> 00:04:14,340
Did Zhang Chengcai come here every day?

96
00:04:14,340 --> 00:04:15,300
Every day.

97
00:04:16,220 --> 00:04:17,020
Was he here tonight?

98
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:17,900
He was.

99
00:04:18,096 --> 00:04:19,020
Sometime after 7 PM.

100
00:04:19,340 --> 00:04:21,060
He sat right there, bawling.

101
00:04:23,820 --> 00:04:25,140
He kept saying

102
00:04:25,140 --> 00:04:26,540
he had let Miss Bai down

103
00:04:26,900 --> 00:04:28,100
and wanted to go with her.

104
00:04:30,180 --> 00:04:31,300
All this over a woman?

105
00:04:32,140 --> 00:04:33,060
Seriously?

106
00:04:34,020 --> 00:04:35,460
If it weren't for you!

107
00:04:35,580 --> 00:04:36,688
Then Madam Zhang showed up,

108
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:37,980
and they got into a huge fight.

109
00:04:38,016 --> 00:04:39,060
Because you're a coward.

110
00:04:39,060 --> 00:04:41,580
- He wanted to cut ties with Madam Zhang.
- Mother.

111
00:04:41,580 --> 00:04:42,340
If you hadn't been

112
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:43,860
my son,

113
00:04:43,860 --> 00:04:45,232
I wouldn't even spare you a glance.

114
00:04:46,620 --> 00:04:49,460
Everyone here, bear witness.

115
00:04:50,620 --> 00:04:54,100
From this day, I, Zhang Chengcai,

116
00:04:54,460 --> 00:04:56,060
am cutting ties with her.

117
00:04:57,340 --> 00:04:58,500
We're done.

118
00:04:59,580 --> 00:05:00,540
Stop right there.

119
00:05:00,540 --> 00:05:01,340
Zhang Chengcai,

120
00:05:01,340 --> 00:05:02,300
you think you can?

121
00:05:02,540 --> 00:05:03,260
You eat my food,

122
00:05:03,260 --> 00:05:03,872
spend my money,

123
00:05:03,904 --> 00:05:05,060
and use it to keep other women.

124
00:05:05,060 --> 00:05:06,580
As long as you're alive,

125
00:05:06,580 --> 00:05:08,220
you'll always be my son.

126
00:05:12,780 --> 00:05:14,540
I'd better be dead!

127
00:05:15,060 --> 00:05:16,540
Watch me expose

128
00:05:16,540 --> 00:05:17,920
all the dirty things you've done.

129
00:05:17,952 --> 00:05:19,460
We'll both go down together!

130
00:05:27,580 --> 00:05:28,900
I dare you!

131
00:05:30,100 --> 00:05:32,540
What dirty things
was Zhang Chengcai talking about?

132
00:05:33,580 --> 00:05:35,100
No idea.

133
00:05:35,104 --> 00:05:37,040
But I'm sure they were hiding something.

134
00:05:39,888 --> 00:05:41,940
What time did Zhang Chengcai
go back to his room?

135
00:05:42,380 --> 00:05:45,260
The dance show had just ended.

136
00:05:46,140 --> 00:05:46,980
Before nine.

137
00:05:47,460 --> 00:05:48,900
About 8:50 PM.

138
00:05:56,780 --> 00:05:57,420
Chief,

139
00:05:57,740 --> 00:05:58,580
we checked.

140
00:05:58,580 --> 00:05:59,620
From 11 PM to 3 AM,

141
00:05:59,620 --> 00:06:01,100
no visitors went up to the third floor.

142
00:06:01,110 --> 00:06:03,140
Unless they were already staying
on the third floor.

143
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,620
Who was staying there?

144
00:06:04,780 --> 00:06:06,380
Other than Zhang Chengcai
and Madam Zhang,

145
00:06:06,464 --> 00:06:07,776
no one else checked in tonight.

146
00:06:08,380 --> 00:06:10,380
Besides Manager Sun,
who delivered the ice,

147
00:06:10,620 --> 00:06:12,340
only Madam Zhang
could've entered Room 306.

148
00:06:13,100 --> 00:06:14,820
You think I killed Zhang Chengcai?

149
00:06:15,060 --> 00:06:16,020
Are you out of your mind?

150
00:06:16,420 --> 00:06:17,860
He's my son.

151
00:06:22,300 --> 00:06:23,580
Why are you so cynical?

152
00:06:24,460 --> 00:06:26,740
Do you have problems
with your own mother?

153
00:06:26,740 --> 00:06:27,660
Watch your mouth.

154
00:06:32,620 --> 00:06:33,540
Was your son

155
00:06:33,900 --> 00:06:35,500
important to you?

156
00:06:35,552 --> 00:06:37,488
(Longevity Pills)
Leader of the Longevity Sect.

157
00:06:45,020 --> 00:06:46,340
True, I founded the sect

158
00:06:47,140 --> 00:06:48,500
and sold Longevity Pills.

159
00:06:48,500 --> 00:06:49,660
But I didn't kill my son.

160
00:06:51,940 --> 00:06:54,050
If I remember correctly,

161
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:54,960
your room faces west.

162
00:06:56,180 --> 00:06:57,700
From that window,

163
00:06:59,350 --> 00:07:01,340
you can see
straight into Bai Lu's bedroom.

164
00:07:02,460 --> 00:07:03,140
So?

165
00:07:03,300 --> 00:07:05,700
So you were always watching Bai Lu,
weren't you?

166
00:07:05,700 --> 00:07:07,980
More precisely,
you were watching your son.

167
00:07:10,820 --> 00:07:11,940
Why would I spy on him?

168
00:07:13,020 --> 00:07:15,020
To make sure he obeyed you

169
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:16,460
and tortured Bai Lu.

170
00:07:16,980 --> 00:07:19,340
Madam Zhang constantly berated him.

171
00:07:19,340 --> 00:07:20,740
She demanded reports on everything.

172
00:07:20,740 --> 00:07:22,060
What he ate,

173
00:07:22,060 --> 00:07:23,340
who he met,

174
00:07:23,340 --> 00:07:24,300
or what he did.

175
00:07:24,460 --> 00:07:26,580
She even made him report on

176
00:07:26,660 --> 00:07:28,340
his intimacy with Bai Lu.

177
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:30,900
What does that have to do
with my son's death?

178
00:07:30,900 --> 00:07:31,860
After Bai Lu died,

179
00:07:31,860 --> 00:07:33,340
Zhang Chengcai broke down.

180
00:07:33,340 --> 00:07:35,100
He threatened to die with you.

181
00:07:36,030 --> 00:07:37,470
I also heard

182
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,980
he wanted to expose

183
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:39,700
your dirty secrets

184
00:07:39,980 --> 00:07:41,100
and drag you down with him.

185
00:07:41,780 --> 00:07:43,020
Don't you dare slander me.

186
00:07:43,300 --> 00:07:44,780
To hush him up...

187
00:07:44,780 --> 00:07:46,300
I killed my own son?

188
00:07:46,300 --> 00:07:47,380
Are you insane?

189
00:07:48,420 --> 00:07:50,020
Madam Zhang is a ruthless one.

190
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:52,820
She always said
anyone who got in her way

191
00:07:53,100 --> 00:07:54,470
deserved to die.

192
00:07:54,740 --> 00:07:56,720
So you slipped into his room

193
00:07:56,730 --> 00:07:57,620
and poisoned him

194
00:07:57,830 --> 00:07:59,130
while his guard was down.

195
00:08:00,848 --> 00:08:01,620
What kind of poison?

196
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:03,340
Cyanide.

197
00:08:03,540 --> 00:08:05,060
It's a very potent poison.

198
00:08:05,260 --> 00:08:07,300
Zhang Chengcai drank poisoned baijiu

199
00:08:07,620 --> 00:08:08,740
and died almost instantly.

200
00:08:09,380 --> 00:08:11,260
Then, you put him in the bathtub,

201
00:08:11,380 --> 00:08:12,180
filled it with water,

202
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:14,100
and placed the glass back in his hand

203
00:08:14,100 --> 00:08:16,980
to make it look like he drowned drunk.

204
00:08:23,420 --> 00:08:24,260
Chief Yuan,

205
00:08:25,180 --> 00:08:27,220
being a policeman
is wasting your talent.

206
00:08:27,430 --> 00:08:28,940
You should be a story teller.

207
00:08:30,340 --> 00:08:31,780
Don't get so worked up.

208
00:08:31,780 --> 00:08:33,460
It's only a theory.

209
00:08:33,660 --> 00:08:34,980
The lab report will be here soon.

210
00:08:35,210 --> 00:08:36,060
We'll see.

211
00:08:44,780 --> 00:08:46,220
Not cyanide poisoning?

212
00:08:47,776 --> 00:08:48,940
What is the cause of death?

213
00:08:49,580 --> 00:08:51,020
It could only be baijiu over ice.

214
00:08:52,380 --> 00:08:53,620
He wasn't poisoned?

215
00:08:54,180 --> 00:08:55,300
Baijiu over ice?

216
00:08:55,900 --> 00:08:57,220
He really drank himself to death?

217
00:08:57,940 --> 00:08:59,680
Madam Zhang didn't do it?

218
00:09:00,980 --> 00:09:01,660
Put that down.

219
00:09:01,660 --> 00:09:02,860
You'll get diabetes.

220
00:09:07,248 --> 00:09:09,380
Whether I stay on as a consultant or not
doesn't matter.

221
00:09:09,460 --> 00:09:10,620
I don't make a living from it.

222
00:09:12,020 --> 00:09:13,380
But her reaction was off.

223
00:09:18,020 --> 00:09:19,020
Arms crossed.

224
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:20,020
Blinking too fast.

225
00:09:20,020 --> 00:09:21,100
Kept touching her nose.

226
00:09:21,220 --> 00:09:22,460
According to criminal psychology,

227
00:09:22,460 --> 00:09:23,340
she was lying.

228
00:09:23,580 --> 00:09:25,060
She's hiding something.

229
00:09:26,660 --> 00:09:28,500
That controlling old liar

230
00:09:28,700 --> 00:09:29,780
put on quite a show!

231
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:36,300
Maybe we should put on one of our own.

232
00:09:38,340 --> 00:09:39,700
Give her a taste

233
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:41,500
of her own medicine.

234
00:09:45,456 --> 00:09:46,820
(Peking Union Medical College
Laboratory Report)

235
00:09:46,820 --> 00:09:48,140
Our apologies, Madam Zhang.

236
00:09:48,260 --> 00:09:49,820
Your son's test results are out.

237
00:09:50,260 --> 00:09:51,420
He wasn't poisoned.

238
00:09:53,340 --> 00:09:55,140
Can you withdraw those officers outside?

239
00:09:55,700 --> 00:09:57,020
Don't you want to know

240
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,460
how your son died?

241
00:09:58,660 --> 00:09:59,620
He took his own life.

242
00:10:00,620 --> 00:10:01,984
You people forced him into it.

243
00:10:05,340 --> 00:10:06,300
Take a look at this.

244
00:10:07,460 --> 00:10:08,660
We found it in his room.

245
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:11,056
You should recognize the handwriting.

246
00:10:11,072 --> 00:10:12,030
(A life or a life.
A son repays for his mother's debt)

247
00:10:12,064 --> 00:10:13,312
He wrote that you killed someone,

248
00:10:13,328 --> 00:10:14,416
and he died to pay your debt.

249
00:10:14,620 --> 00:10:15,660
If he killed himself,

250
00:10:15,940 --> 00:10:17,296
then we didn't drive him to it.

251
00:10:17,820 --> 00:10:18,380
You did.

252
00:10:18,380 --> 00:10:19,100
Nonsense!

253
00:10:24,380 --> 00:10:25,700
Bai Lu bewitched him.

254
00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:28,180
That vixen

255
00:10:29,216 --> 00:10:31,120
wouldn't let him go,
even after she died.

256
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:35,860
What debt was Zhang Chengcai
talking about?

257
00:10:36,260 --> 00:10:37,380
None of your business.

258
00:10:39,220 --> 00:10:40,500
Yes, it's none of our business.

259
00:10:41,660 --> 00:10:42,860
It's very much yours,

260
00:10:42,860 --> 00:10:43,580
Madam Zhang.

261
00:10:46,432 --> 00:10:48,768
Don't you think these past few days
have been rather strange?

262
00:10:51,818 --> 00:10:52,858
You don't mean...

263
00:10:57,500 --> 00:10:58,780
First, Bai Lu died.

264
00:10:58,980 --> 00:11:00,180
Then your son.

265
00:11:00,580 --> 00:11:02,100
One after another.

266
00:11:02,380 --> 00:11:03,300
Enough.

267
00:11:03,300 --> 00:11:04,420
I have to tell her.

268
00:11:04,780 --> 00:11:05,860
Everyone's watching

269
00:11:05,860 --> 00:11:06,540
this case now.

270
00:11:06,620 --> 00:11:07,140
Don't forget

271
00:11:07,140 --> 00:11:08,140
that's is a haunted house.

272
00:11:14,100 --> 00:11:15,420
Don't you try to trick me.

273
00:11:42,976 --> 00:11:44,660
There's an evil spirit in the southeast.

274
00:11:54,820 --> 00:11:55,780
It's Zhang Chengcai.

275
00:11:56,460 --> 00:11:57,900
He says you killed him.

276
00:11:58,100 --> 00:11:59,620
He blames you for drowning him.

277
00:11:59,620 --> 00:12:00,620
I didn't kill him.

278
00:12:00,620 --> 00:12:01,900
Why would he blame me?

279
00:12:09,780 --> 00:12:12,780
He says you turned his death
into a spectacle.

280
00:12:15,020 --> 00:12:15,860
Chengcai,

281
00:12:16,660 --> 00:12:17,620
don't blame me.

282
00:12:17,940 --> 00:12:20,580
I have to stay alive too.
I have to make a living.

283
00:12:20,580 --> 00:12:21,300
Don't move.

284
00:12:23,820 --> 00:12:24,700
There's someone else.

285
00:12:24,700 --> 00:12:26,140
Long hair. She's singing.

286
00:12:26,860 --> 00:12:27,860
It's Bai Lu's voice.

287
00:12:27,860 --> 00:12:29,180
I... I didn't kill Bai Lu.

288
00:12:29,180 --> 00:12:29,980
Who did?

289
00:12:29,980 --> 00:12:30,860
She has long hair.

290
00:12:30,860 --> 00:12:32,220
She says it was you.

291
00:12:32,220 --> 00:12:32,496
Not me!

292
00:12:32,512 --> 00:12:33,900
You turned her into a wandering soul.

293
00:12:33,900 --> 00:12:34,220
Not me.

294
00:12:34,220 --> 00:12:35,232
She says you killed her.

295
00:12:35,264 --> 00:12:36,220
She says it was you!

296
00:12:36,220 --> 00:12:37,060
It was an accident.

297
00:12:37,060 --> 00:12:37,940
What accident?

298
00:12:37,940 --> 00:12:39,060
She was burned.

299
00:12:39,100 --> 00:12:40,420
It wasn't me!

300
00:12:44,540 --> 00:12:46,580
My son's dead!

301
00:12:47,180 --> 00:12:51,060
We're even now!

302
00:12:51,180 --> 00:12:53,940
Your death had nothing to do with me.

303
00:12:53,940 --> 00:12:54,940
Don't come after me.

304
00:12:54,940 --> 00:12:56,020
It wasn't me.

305
00:12:56,020 --> 00:12:57,740
What do you want from me?

306
00:12:58,020 --> 00:12:58,700
What do you want?

307
00:12:58,700 --> 00:12:59,300
Who?

308
00:12:59,540 --> 00:13:00,140
Who was burned?

309
00:13:00,140 --> 00:13:01,580
It has nothing to do with me.

310
00:13:01,580 --> 00:13:02,740
Don't come after me!

311
00:13:02,740 --> 00:13:04,420
Who was burned?

312
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:06,100
Zhenzhen!

313
00:13:16,660 --> 00:13:17,460
Who's Zhenzhen?

314
00:13:23,740 --> 00:13:24,860
You killed her?

315
00:13:31,740 --> 00:13:32,940
If you won't talk,

316
00:13:33,300 --> 00:13:34,660
we'll find out for ourselves

317
00:13:34,940 --> 00:13:36,260
now that we have her name.

318
00:14:07,620 --> 00:14:08,620
Strong on the first sip.

319
00:14:09,060 --> 00:14:09,940
Mild on the finish.

320
00:14:10,860 --> 00:14:11,540
Distinctive.

321
00:14:11,760 --> 00:14:13,100
Manager Sun created this cocktail

322
00:14:13,100 --> 00:14:15,300
for Miss Bai Lu's wedding.

323
00:14:15,580 --> 00:14:16,340
It's called Bai Lu.

324
00:14:17,248 --> 00:14:18,460
Does it have a strong kick?

325
00:14:18,544 --> 00:14:19,180
It's low-proof.

326
00:14:19,420 --> 00:14:20,780
Young ladies can drink a few.

327
00:14:21,820 --> 00:14:22,700
Try this one, too.

328
00:14:23,220 --> 00:14:23,750
It's new.

329
00:14:35,740 --> 00:14:36,220
Soft.

330
00:14:36,928 --> 00:14:38,420
Slightly astringent on the finish.

331
00:14:38,896 --> 00:14:39,936
What is this called?

332
00:14:42,300 --> 00:14:42,940
Zhenzhen.

333
00:14:44,448 --> 00:14:45,744
You were in love with her,

334
00:14:45,776 --> 00:14:47,056
but you never won her heart.

335
00:14:48,740 --> 00:14:49,980
You can taste that?

336
00:14:51,740 --> 00:14:52,860
What does Zhenzhen do?

337
00:14:54,780 --> 00:14:55,420
A dancer.

338
00:14:55,980 --> 00:14:57,380
She used to work at a dance hall,

339
00:14:57,780 --> 00:14:59,040
but quit after only a few days.

340
00:14:59,580 --> 00:15:00,660
I went to her place,

341
00:15:01,260 --> 00:15:01,940
but she was gone.

342
00:15:03,620 --> 00:15:04,860
A dancer

343
00:15:05,140 --> 00:15:06,700
meets all kinds of men every day.

344
00:15:06,940 --> 00:15:07,820
Maybe she met

345
00:15:07,820 --> 00:15:09,220
some wealthy gentleman she liked

346
00:15:09,620 --> 00:15:10,580
and left with him.

347
00:15:10,640 --> 00:15:12,752
Better than living a hard life
with you. Am I right?

348
00:15:15,260 --> 00:15:16,100
I hope she's happy.

349
00:15:16,860 --> 00:15:18,300
What if she's dead?

350
00:15:22,064 --> 00:15:23,136
He's a homicide detective.

351
00:15:23,152 --> 00:15:24,370
That's the cop in him talking.

352
00:15:24,380 --> 00:15:25,700
I think

353
00:15:25,700 --> 00:15:27,280
she probably ran off with some rich man.

354
00:15:28,020 --> 00:15:29,060
What if

355
00:15:29,740 --> 00:15:31,340
she were murdered?

356
00:15:31,340 --> 00:15:33,180
If you're a man, you have two choices.

357
00:15:33,180 --> 00:15:34,100
Die for her,

358
00:15:34,660 --> 00:15:35,540
or avenge her.

359
00:15:45,400 --> 00:15:47,060
The night Zhenzhen disappeared,

360
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:49,780
you saw Madam Zhang talk to her.

361
00:15:50,740 --> 00:15:52,380
They seemed to get along well.

362
00:15:52,464 --> 00:15:54,656
(Zhenzhen)
You didn't hear what they talked about.

363
00:15:55,260 --> 00:15:56,860
But you suspected her disappearance

364
00:15:56,860 --> 00:15:58,128
had something to do with them.

365
00:15:58,416 --> 00:16:00,700
That night, you got Zhang Chengcai
completely drunk.

366
00:16:00,700 --> 00:16:01,740
After he passed out,

367
00:16:02,180 --> 00:16:04,060
he let slip how Zhenzhen died.

368
00:16:11,740 --> 00:16:13,740
Jinshil No. 1 wasn't making money,

369
00:16:13,824 --> 00:16:15,620
so Madam Zhang
started the Longevity Sect.

370
00:16:16,460 --> 00:16:18,300
She had Bai Lu pose
as the Holy Maiden.

371
00:16:18,780 --> 00:16:20,260
They used green flames

372
00:16:20,460 --> 00:16:22,144
and fireproof asbestos cloth

373
00:16:22,160 --> 00:16:24,800
to make it look like the Holy Maiden
could walk through fire unharmed,

374
00:16:24,848 --> 00:16:27,088
then tricked the followers
into buying Longevity Pills.

375
00:16:31,420 --> 00:16:33,580
But later, Bai Lu refused to
go along with it,

376
00:16:34,140 --> 00:16:35,900
so Madam Zhang turned to Zhenzhen.

377
00:16:37,780 --> 00:16:39,060
How much do you make

378
00:16:39,580 --> 00:16:40,540
dancing all night?

379
00:16:41,380 --> 00:16:42,220
Five coppers.

380
00:16:44,460 --> 00:16:45,380
Unfortunately,

381
00:16:45,940 --> 00:16:48,260
Zhenzhen didn't follow
Madam Zheng's instructions.

382
00:16:48,580 --> 00:16:49,500
She wore silk stockings.

383
00:16:49,900 --> 00:16:51,980
The wind blew sparks onto her ankles.

384
00:16:52,580 --> 00:16:53,660
The wind was so strong

385
00:16:53,680 --> 00:16:55,560
that her whole body
was soon engulfed in flames.

386
00:16:55,728 --> 00:16:57,060
To keep the truth from getting out,

387
00:16:57,580 --> 00:17:00,340
Madam Zhang and Zhang Chengcai
kept deceiving the crowd.

388
00:17:00,980 --> 00:17:03,300
The Holy Maiden sacrifices herself

389
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:05,860
for the faithful's eternal life!

390
00:17:06,300 --> 00:17:09,120
- The Holy Maiden sacrifices herself
- The Holy Maiden sacrifices herself

391
00:17:09,130 --> 00:17:11,690
- for the faithful's eternal life!
- for the faithful's eternal life!

392
00:17:11,700 --> 00:17:13,930
- The Holy Maiden sacrifices herself
- The Holy Maiden sacrifices herself

393
00:17:13,940 --> 00:17:16,540
- for the faithful's eternal life!
- for the faithful's eternal life!

394
00:17:17,060 --> 00:17:19,140
For the faithful's eternal life!

395
00:17:19,140 --> 00:17:21,370
- The Holy Maiden sacrifices herself
- The Holy Maiden sacrifices herself

396
00:17:21,380 --> 00:17:24,420
- for the faithful's eternal life!
- for the faithful's eternal life!

397
00:17:24,740 --> 00:17:26,460
They stood there

398
00:17:26,512 --> 00:17:27,872
watching Zhenzhen burn to death.

399
00:17:30,220 --> 00:17:31,660
So to avenge her,

400
00:17:31,776 --> 00:17:32,740
you told Zhang Chengcai

401
00:17:32,740 --> 00:17:34,208
that baijiu tastes better over ice.

402
00:17:34,384 --> 00:17:35,152
Didn't you?

403
00:17:35,980 --> 00:17:36,980
What if I did?

404
00:17:37,380 --> 00:17:38,100
Is that a crime?

405
00:17:46,300 --> 00:17:47,140
It was you!

406
00:17:47,860 --> 00:17:49,180
You killed my son!

407
00:17:49,580 --> 00:17:50,540
Give him back!

408
00:17:51,220 --> 00:17:52,100
Give me back my son!

409
00:17:52,100 --> 00:17:53,620
Let go! Give me back my son!

410
00:17:53,620 --> 00:17:54,300
Take her away.

411
00:17:54,300 --> 00:17:55,860
You killed my son!

412
00:17:56,020 --> 00:17:57,540
I won't let you get away with this.

413
00:17:57,540 --> 00:17:58,500
It was you!

414
00:17:58,500 --> 00:17:59,900
What does it have to do with me?

415
00:18:00,020 --> 00:18:01,660
He had a short life.

416
00:18:02,672 --> 00:18:03,820
He drank himself to death.

417
00:18:09,180 --> 00:18:10,000
He deserved this.

418
00:18:12,900 --> 00:18:14,060
But lividity at this stage

419
00:18:14,060 --> 00:18:15,340
is usually dark red.

420
00:18:16,100 --> 00:18:17,260
His was bright red.

421
00:18:27,620 --> 00:18:28,340
Manager Sun.

422
00:18:29,184 --> 00:18:30,240
Young Master Zhao.

423
00:18:30,340 --> 00:18:31,060
Chief Yuan.

424
00:18:32,020 --> 00:18:33,340
The bartender won't be charged

425
00:18:33,340 --> 00:18:35,020
over Zhang Chengcai's death, will he?

426
00:18:36,180 --> 00:18:37,340
He only suggested

427
00:18:37,340 --> 00:18:38,420
a way to drink.

428
00:18:38,540 --> 00:18:39,380
Legally speaking,

429
00:18:39,380 --> 00:18:41,440
Zhang Chengcai's death
has nothing to do with him.

430
00:18:41,580 --> 00:18:42,300
That's a relief.

431
00:18:42,368 --> 00:18:43,680
You seem worried about him?

432
00:18:43,740 --> 00:18:45,100
He's a good kid.

433
00:18:45,100 --> 00:18:47,060
It'd be a shame if he went to prison

434
00:18:47,664 --> 00:18:48,780
because of Zhang Chengcai.

435
00:18:50,060 --> 00:18:51,140
He won't.

436
00:18:51,830 --> 00:18:52,900
You might.

437
00:18:57,020 --> 00:18:58,420
I don't understand.

438
00:18:58,860 --> 00:18:59,860
Zhang Chengcai

439
00:19:00,560 --> 00:19:01,860
was killed by you, wasn't he?

440
00:19:03,660 --> 00:19:05,940
(End of Episode 17)

441
00:19:07,120 --> 00:19:08,760
♪Side by side,
we journey through this life♪

442
00:19:08,760 --> 00:19:10,300
♪Troubled times
are but a laughing matter♪

443
00:19:10,300 --> 00:19:11,550
♪However, the world changes♪

444
00:19:11,550 --> 00:19:13,470
♪You'll still be by my side♪

445
00:19:13,470 --> 00:19:15,160
♪Side by side,
we journey through this life♪

446
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:16,730
♪Praise and blame come and go♪

447
00:19:16,730 --> 00:19:18,300
♪If this is my final chapter♪

448
00:19:18,300 --> 00:19:20,800
♪I'll solve this mystery with you♪
